Fig. 7
). Tegmina black, with light brown stripe along upper (posterior) margin. Fore and mid legs blackish brown. Hind femur black, with light brown stripe along upper side and two light brown spots in the lower side of femur; dorsal genicular lobes blackish brown, ventral genicular lobes black (
Fig. 7
). Hind tibia black with yellow ring in basal third; dorsal spines black with yellowish base (
Fig. 8
